<item>
            <title>[HTTPCLIENT-2077] Migration from HttpClient v4.5.x to v5.0 causes NTLM proxy authentication failure</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-2077</link>
                <project id="12310360" key="HTTPCLIENT">HttpComponents HttpClient</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Upgrade of HttpClient from v4.5.x to v5.0 causes a NTLM proxy authentication failure (s. attached test class&#160;&lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13001184/13001184_NtlmProxyAuthenticationTest.java&quot; title=&quot;NtlmProxyAuthenticationTest.java attached to HTTPCLIENT-2077&quot;&gt;NtlmProxyAuthenticationTest.java&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#160;with generated&#160;log file&#160;&lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13001183/13001183_NtlmProxyAuthenticationTest.log&quot; title=&quot;NtlmProxyAuthenticationTest.log attached to HTTPCLIENT-2077&quot;&gt;NtlmProxyAuthenticationTest.log&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Error logged:&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
01:27:20.360 [main] DEBUG org.apache.hc.client5.http.impl.auth.HttpAuthenticator - Authentication failed
----------------------------------------
407 authenticationrequired
&#160;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The same class implemented with HttpClient v4.5.x does not have any proxy issues and connects to the target as expected.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
